                  text: "## Key Metrics\n\nActive users reached 45 million, a 22% increase. Monthly recurring revenue hit $350M. Net promoter score improved from 62 to 71. Employee headcount grew to 8,500 across 12 offices globally. R&D investment was $840M, representing 20% of revenue.",
